        </item>
        <item>
            <title>毋须用电，只用弹簧减轻骑单车负担，日本新技术 Reloda 省力最高达 20%</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/20/reloda/life-tech/bike/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=reloda</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/20/reloda/life-tech/bike/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 20 Apr 2025 06:59:28 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[个人移动装置]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
